 families of polytopes resulting from\nthese inequalities are part of the new class of so-called lineup polytopes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 May 2021 17:56:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Jun 2021 10:54:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-10"}
