 that the BSPs are not, in most cases,\nthe dominant contributor to the accreted stellar halo of each galaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 May 2021 17:59:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Jun 2022 23:08:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-22"}
