rately determine the actual\ncritical black hole mass corresponding to the onset of neutron star destruction\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 May 2021 18:34:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2022 21:53:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-27"}
