eric model is not able to account for the current\nset of optical prompt detections that have been made and additional radiative\nmechanisms are needed to explain these prompt optical observations. These\nfindings show the importance of conducting global radiative transfer\nsimulations using hydrodynamically calculated jet structures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 May 2021 18:35:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Sep 2021 09:45:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-15"}
