ecific measurement paves the way to\nwidespread application for observations of transient hole dynamics localized in\nspace and time in molecules and thus to charge transfer phenomena that are\nfundamental in chemical and material physics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 May 2021 18:48:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-08"}
