et management. We found our\nscore-based optimal portfolios less concentrated than the mean-variance\nportfolio and much less risky in terms of ranking.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 May 2021 22:29:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-17"}
