oposed approach outperforms benchmark schemes in terms of\nenergy efficiency (EE), contributing to underwater emergency communications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 May 2021 06:04:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 May 2023 01:46:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-03"}
