ly universe. We find that all the necessary conditions for\nthe axion-CMB scenario can be satisfied in some parameter regions for massless\n$S$ fields, typically $N\\sim 10^{19}$ and the mass of $B$-$L$ gauge boson\naround $5-10$ TeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 May 2021 12:49:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-22"}
